            <html:p>The notions of <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001H/" title="Contractible type" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001H/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001H" type="local">contractible</fr:link> and <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" title="Proposition" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I" type="local">propositional</fr:link> types generate an infinite hierarchy of <html:em>truncation levels</html:em> expressing the point after which higher identifications become trivial.</html:p>
