   <fr:tree show-metadata="false" toc="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling/" title="Jon Sterling" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:date><fr:year>2023</fr:year><fr:month>12</fr:month><fr:day>31</fr:day></fr:date><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
 <html:p>We proceed by induction on the <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001F/" title="Indexing of truncation levels" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001F/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001F" type="local">truncation level</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>: when <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n=-2]]></fr:tex>, we recall that the <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-002U/" title="The identity map is contractible" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-002U/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-002U" type="local">identity map is contractible</fr:link>, and in the inductive step we apply the <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-002T/" title="truncation is upward closed" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-002T/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-002T" type="local">upward closure of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>-truncation</fr:link> to each <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001Q/" title="Fiber" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001Q/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001Q" type="local">fiber</fr:link> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[1_{A}]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>
