            <fr:title text="truncation is upward closed"><fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001G/" title="n-truncated type" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001G/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001G" type="local">truncation</fr:link> is upward closed</fr:title>
