            <fr:meta name="source">
  
  
  <fr:link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-002T.agda" type="external">erct-002T.agda</fr:link>
</fr:meta>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter><html:p>If a type <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001G/" title="n-truncated type" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001G/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001G" type="local"><html:span style="white-space: nowrap"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>-truncated</html:span></fr:link>, then it is also <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001G/" title="n-truncated type" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001G/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001G" type="local"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n+1]]></fr:tex>-truncated</fr:link>.</html:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree show-metadata="false" toc="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling/" title="Jon Sterling" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:date><fr:year>2023</fr:year><fr:month>12</fr:month><fr:day>31</fr:day></fr:date><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
 <html:p>By induction on the <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001F/" title="Indexing of truncation levels" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001F/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001F" type="local">truncation level</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>, with two base cases given by <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001K/" title="contractible types are propositions" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001K/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001K" type="local">Lemma <fr:contextual-number uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001K/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001K" /></fr:link> and <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001L/" title="propositions are sets" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001L/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001L" type="local">Lemma <fr:contextual-number uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001L/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001L" /></fr:link>.</html:p>
</fr:mainmatter></fr:tree>
 
</fr:mainmatter>
