              </fr:author>
            </fr:authors>
            <fr:date>
              <fr:year>2023</fr:year>
              <fr:month>12</fr:month>
              <fr:day>20</fr:day>
            </fr:date>
            <fr:uri>https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001P/</fr:uri>
            <fr:display-uri>https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001P</fr:display-uri>
            <fr:route>/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001P/</fr:route>
            <fr:title text="Being n-truncated is a proposition">Being <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001G/" title="n-truncated type" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001G/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001G" type="local"><html:span style="white-space: nowrap"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>-truncated</html:span></fr:link> is a <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" title="Proposition" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I" type="local">proposition</fr:link></fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Lemma</fr:taxon>
            <fr:meta name="source">
  
  
  <fr:link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-001P.agda" type="external">erct-001P.agda</fr:link>
</fr:meta>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter><html:p>It is a <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" title="Proposition" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I" type="local">proposition</fr:link> that a given type <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001G/" title="n-truncated type" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001G/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001G" type="local"><html:span style="white-space: nowrap"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>-truncated</html:span></fr:link>.</html:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree show-metadata="false" toc="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling/" title="Jon Sterling" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:date><fr:year>2023</fr:year><fr:month>12</fr:month><fr:day>20</fr:day></fr:date><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
  <html:p>We proceed by induction on the <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001F/" title="Indexing of truncation levels" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001F/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001F" type="local">truncation level</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>
  <html:ol><html:li>When <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n=-2]]></fr:tex>, we recall from <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001N/" title="Being contractible is a proposition" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001N/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001N" type="local">Lemma <fr:contextual-number uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001N/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001N" /></fr:link> that being <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001H/" title="Contractible type" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001H/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001H" type="local">contractible</fr:link> is a <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" title="Proposition" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I" type="local">proposition</fr:link>.</html:li>
    <html:li>When <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n=-1]]></fr:tex>, we recall from <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001O/" title="Being a proposition is a proposition" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001O/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001O" type="local">Lemma <fr:contextual-number uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001O/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001O" /></fr:link> that
      being a <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" title="Proposition" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I" type="local">proposition</fr:link> is a <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" title="Proposition" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I" type="local">proposition</fr:link>.</html:li>
    <html:li>For <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n \geq  0]]></fr:tex>, we assume by induction that being <html:span style="white-space: nowrap"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n-1]]></fr:tex>-truncated</html:span> is a <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" title="Proposition" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I" type="local">proposition</fr:link> to prove that being <html:span style="white-space: nowrap"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>-truncated</html:span> is a <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" title="Proposition" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I" type="local">proposition</fr:link>. In other words, we must show that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x,y:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x,y:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x,y:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x,y:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}\mathsf {isTruncated}\,
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen n-1\right \rparen \mathclose {}
\,A]]></fr:tex> is a <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" title="Proposition" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I" type="local">proposition</fr:link>. By our inductive hypothesis, this is a dependent product of <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" title="Proposition" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I" type="local">propositions</fr:link> (<fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001B/" title="Dependent product of propositions" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001B/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001B" type="local">Corollary <fr:contextual-number uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001B/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001B" /></fr:link>).</html:li></html:ol>
</fr:mainmatter></fr:tree>
 
</fr:mainmatter>
